BC Image Alias extension README

What is the BC Image Alias extension?
================================

BC Image Alias is a true eZ Publish extension
that provides commandline script, workflow event,
cronjob parts, class methods, module views and
admin siteaccess content structure menu items to
create, remove and regenerate content object
image alias variations.


BC Image Alias version
=======================

The current version of BC Image Alias is 0.0.23
Last Major update: December 11, 2011

You can find details about changes for this
version in doc/changelogs/CHANGELOG-0.0.23


